          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "text": "Pear Cut Promise Rings",
            "heading_tag": "h1"
          }
        },
        "richtext_Ve7WCq": {
          "type": "richtext",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>A pear cut promise ring offer a distinctive and emotional way to represent love and commitment. Also known as a teardrop shape, the pear cut combines a soft rounded edge with a single point, creating a silhouette that feels elegant, expressive and deeply personal.This unique shape is designed to catch light beautifully while also creating a flattering, elongated look on the finger. Its tapered design can make the stone appear larger and more refined, adding to its appeal as a modern yet timeless choice.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
